snippet.title: Dangerous Golf - Comedy Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
A look at some of the funnier moments in Dangerous Golf, the game where destruction and over the top trickshots are the way to score big. Along the way, Smash up the toilets, make a big mess in the Kitchen, destroy priceless antiques in the Palace. This is golf played indoors where the more expensive the object the higher its game value.     

https://store.playstation.com/#!/en-us/games/dangerous-golf/cid=UP1898-CUSA05385_00-TFEDANGEROUSGOLF?smcid=psblog:::ps-blog-tag-playstation-store
